ANNOUNCE
  Broadcast a message to all active countries.

SYNTAX
  announce <message>
  anno     <message>

DESCRIPTION
  Sends a public announcement that all active players can read.
  Announcements appear in the game news and are visible to everyone
  when they log in and check announcements.

  Use 'telegram' to send a private message to a specific country.
  Use 'announce' for public declarations (war warnings, trade
  offers, diplomatic statements).

EXAMPLE
  announce Beware: Country 3 is expanding west!
  anno Selling 500 food at capital, contact me

SEE ALSO
  telegram  read  relations  declare
